-- Gunmen Assassinate Mayor-Elect in Southern Colombia, Efe Says
-- B y   E d u a r d o   T h o m s o n
-- 2011-12-31T19:53:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-31/gunmen-assassinate-mayor-elect-in-southern-colombia-efe-says.html
Jaime Chazatar, mayor-elect of the
municipality of Santa Cruz-Guachaves in Southern Colombia, was
killed by gunmen, the Spanish-language newswire Efe reported.  Two men shot Chazatar in front of his home today, Efe said,
citing Fabio Trujillo, secretary of the government in the
Colombian department of Narino.  Chazatar was supposed to assume the position of mayor of
Santa Cruz-Guachaves tomorrow, Efe reported. He was elected in
October, running as a candidate for the Indigenous Authorities
of Colombia party, Efe said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduardo Thomson in Santiago at 
 ethomson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
